---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`${SITE_TITLE} | Projects`} description="Selected projects and engineering case studies." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main style="max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 16px;">
      <h1>Projects & Case Studies</h1>
      
      <div class="projects-container">
        <article class="project">
          <h2>Smart Industrial Monitoring System</h2>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> Lead Software Engineer</p>
          <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> Python, MQTT, Node-RED, PostgreSQL, React</p>
          <p>
            Designed and implemented a real-time monitoring platform for industrial equipment. 
            Built an edge computing solution using Raspberry Pi with MQTT protocol for sensor data collection. 
            Developed a responsive web dashboard for real-time analytics and predictive maintenance alerts. 
            Reduced mean time to failure by 40% through early anomaly detection.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <h2>IoT Data Pipeline Architecture</h2>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> Software Architect</p>
          <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> AWS IoT Core, Lambda, Kinesis, Docker, Kubernetes</p>
          <p>
            Architected a scalable cloud-based data pipeline handling 100,000+ messages/second. 
            Implemented edge-to-cloud hybrid solution with local processing capabilities. 
            Designed data transformation and enrichment services. Achieved 99.99% uptime SLA 
            and reduced latency by 60%.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <h2>Embedded Device Firmware Development</h2>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> Embedded Systems Engineer</p>
          <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> C/C++, STM32, CAN bus, Modbus, ARM Cortex-M</p>
          <p>
            Developed firmware for multi-protocol industrial controller supporting CAN bus and Modbus. 
            Implemented real-time processing with hard deadlines and interrupt handling. 
            Optimized memory usage for resource-constrained environment (512KB RAM). 
            Achieved 50% reduction in power consumption through efficient scheduling.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <h2>Mobile Data Collection App</h2>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> Full Stack Developer</p>
          <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> React Native, TypeScript, Firebase, Offline-First Architecture</p>
          <p>
            Built offline-first mobile app for field data collection in areas with poor connectivity. 
            Implemented local SQLite database with cloud synchronization. 
            Developed push notification system for real-time alerts. 
            Used by 500+ field technicians across multiple sites.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <h2>Open Source IIoT Framework</h2>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> Creator & Maintainer</p>
          <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> Python, MQTT, Docker, GitHub</p>
          <p>
            Designed an open-source framework simplifying IoT application development. 
            1000+ GitHub stars, active community contributing use cases and extensions. 
            Documented comprehensive API and deployment guides. 
            Framework adopted by startups and enterprises for rapid prototyping.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 48px;">Technical Focus Areas</h2>
      <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
        <li><strong>Industrial IoT Solutions:</strong> End-to-end system design from sensors to cloud</li>
        <li><strong>Real-time Systems:</strong> Low-latency processing and deterministic behavior</li>
        <li><strong>Edge Computing:</strong> On-device processing and local intelligence</li>
        <li><strong>Protocol Integration:</strong> MQTT, CoAP, OPC UA, Modbus, CAN</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud Architecture:</strong> AWS, Azure, serverless, microservices</li>
        <li><strong>Data Pipeline:</strong> Stream processing, analytics, storage optimization</li>
      </ul>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .projects-container {
    display: grid;
    gap: 32px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .project {
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.02);
  }

  .project h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #2563eb;
  }

  .project p {
    margin: 8px 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 16px 0;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  li {
    margin: 12px 0;
  }
</style>